nd\nthe purpose of a detector for HEP. A first detector with such a mechanical\nstructure has been built and shipped to IHEP, preliminary results from\noperation (e.g. current stability, discharges, temperature and humidity\ncorrelation) of the detectors will be also presented in this talk.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 May 2020 11:52:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 25 May 2020 13:58:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-26"}
